            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 text-center">The Evolving Social Engineering Threat</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
                Social engineering exploits human trust to bypass technical security controls. The rise of AI-powered attacks has made these threats more sophisticated and harder to detect. This section details the common attack vectors and highlights specific vulnerabilities within key Australian industries.
            </p>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-12">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-cyan-700 mb-2">Phishing & BEC</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Deceptive emails or messages from seemingly trusted sources to steal credentials or initiate fraudulent transactions. Business Email Compromise (BEC) is a highly damaging variant.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-cyan-700 mb-2">Baiting</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Luring victims with tempting offers (e.g., free software, infected USB drives) to install malware or gain system access.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-cyan-700 mb-2">Pretexting</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Creating a fabricated scenario or "pretext" to manipulate a target into divulging information or performing an action.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-cyan-700 mb-2">AI-Powered Attacks</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Using AI for voice cloning and deepfakes to create highly convincing impersonations, making detection extremely difficult.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

